<plot>In the tradition of Roald Dahl or O.Henry, this strange little psychological thriller begins when a New Yorker stops in a small Pennsylvania town with a flat tire only trapped in the local bar where he is acused of being a hit and run driver who killed one of their patrons. As the locals interrogate and threaten our protagonist we are lead through a series of psycholical twists and turns, leading to a very surprise ending.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?070706</url></doc>
